Package it.unipr.sowide.java.classes

Annotation Interface TypePreamble

@Target(TYPE) public @interface TypePreamble
The annotation TypePreamble defines the main information about a document.

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements
    Modifier and Type
    Required Element
    Description
    String
    author
    Gets the author's first and last names.
    String
    date
    Gets the document creation date.
    String[]
    reviewers
    Gets the first and last names of the reviewers.
